"case in which the target number is not present:\n"
"\n"
"<ol>\n"
"\t\n"
"    <li> Let <code>min = 0</code> and <code>max = n-1</code>.</li>\n"
"\n"
"\t\t<li> If <code>max < min</code>, then stop: <code>target</code> is\n"
"\t\t\t\t not present in <code>array</code>. Return\n"
"\t\t\t\t <code>-1</code>.</li>\n"
"\n"
"    <li> Compute <code>guess</code> as the average of <code>max</code>\n"
"\t\t\t\t and <code>min</code>, rounded down (so that it is an\n"
"\t\t\t\t integer).</li>\n"
"\n"
