"\t\t\t\t target</code>, then set <code>min = guess + 1</code>.</li>\n"
"\n"
"    <li> Otherwise, the guess was too high.  Set <code>max = guess -\n"
"\t\t\t\t 1</code>.</li>\n"
"\n"
"\t\t<li> Go back to step 2.</li>\n"
"\n"
"</ol></p>\n"
