"\t<li><em>(Optional)</em> Sign up as a coach on Khan Academy and add your students. That will make it easy for you to track their progress. <a href=\"/coach-res/become-a-coach/coach-set-up/a/setting-up-your-coach-account\">See this guide for instructions</a>.&nbsp;</li>\n"
