"<h3>Ancient symbols made new</h3>\n"
"\n"
"<p>The exterior of the divination bowl is covered with both inscriptions and signs of the&nbsp;zodiac. Some of the zodiac signs&nbsp;are represented with&nbsp;traditional figures, but others&nbsp;are more unusual.</p>\n"
