"<p>When you think of Hell, what images fill your imagination? &nbsp;Your mind might first conjure up a monstrous satanic figure, and then you may further fill in the picture with other beastly devils that roam around torturing damned sinners, who in turn cry out with pain and regret.</p>\n"
