"&=5 \\cdot \\dfrac{2\\text{ 単位}}{1} \\\\\\\\\n"
"&=10\\text{ 単位}\n"
"\\end{align}$"

msgid ""
"We can perform a unit conversion to figure out how many units we need to represent $600\\text{ km}$:\n"
