"$60\\text{ m}$ を表現するために必要な単位はどれだけかを求めるために，もう一度単位の変換をすることができます:\n"
"\n"
"$\\qquad\\begin{align} \n"
"&~~~~60\\cancel{\\text{ m}} \\cdot \n"
"\\dfrac{3\\text{ 単位}}{18\\cancel{\\text{ m}}} \\\\\\\\\n"
"&=60 \\cdot \\dfrac{3\\text{ 単位}}{18} \\\\\\\\\n"
"&=10\\text{ 単位}\n"
"\\end{align}$"

msgid ""
"We can perform a unit conversion to figure out how many units we need to represent $6\\text{ mm}$:\n"
"\n"
"$\\qquad\\begin{align} \n"
"&~~~~6\\cancel{\\text{ mm}} \\cdot \n"
"\\dfrac{4\\text{ units}}{3\\cancel{\\text{ mm}}} \\\\\\\\\n"
"&=6 \\cdot \\dfrac{4\\text{ units}}{3} \\\\\\\\\n"
"&=8\\text{ units}\n"
"\\end{align}$"
