"$6\\text{ mm}$ を表現するために必要な単位はどれだけかを求めるために，もう一度単位の変換をすることができます:\n"
"\n"
"$\\qquad\\begin{align} \n"
"&~~~~6\\cancel{\\text{ mm}} \\cdot \n"
"\\dfrac{4\\text{ 単位}}{3\\cancel{\\text{ mm}}} \\\\\\\\\n"
"&=6 \\cdot \\dfrac{4\\text{ 単位}}{3} \\\\\\\\\n"
"&=8\\text{ 単位}\n"
"\\end{align}$"

msgid ""
"We can perform a unit conversion to figure out how many units we need to represent $7.5\\text{ mm}$:\n"
"\n"
"$\\qquad\\begin{align} \n"
"&~~~~7.5\\cancel{\\text{ mm}} \\cdot \n"
"\\dfrac{2\\text{ units}}{1\\cancel{\\text{ mm}}} \\\\\\\\\n"
"&=7.5 \\cdot \\dfrac{2\\text{ units}}{1} \\\\\\\\\n"
"&=15\\text{ units}\n"
"\\end{align}$"
msgstr ""
"$7.5\\text{ mm}$ を表現するために必要な単位はどれだけかを求めるために，もう一度単位の変換をすることができます:\n"
"\n"
"$\\qquad\\begin{align} \n"
"&~~~~7.5\\cancel{\\text{ mm}} \\cdot \n"
"\\dfrac{2\\text{ 単位}}{1\\cancel{\\text{ mm}}} \\\\\\\\\n"
"&=7.5 \\cdot \\dfrac{2\\text{ 単位}}{1} \\\\\\\\\n"
"&=15\\text{ 単位}\n"
"\\end{align}$"

msgid ""
"We can perform a unit conversion to figure out how many units we need to represent $8\\text{ m}$:\n"
"\n"
"$\\qquad\\begin{align} \n"
"&~~~~8\\cancel{\\text{ m}} \\cdot \n"
"\\dfrac{3\\text{ units}}{4\\cancel{\\text{ m}}} \\\\\\\\\n"
"&=8 \\cdot \\dfrac{3\\text{ units}}{4} \\\\\\\\\n"
"&=6\\text{ units}\n"
"\\end{align}$"
