msgid "You can add, subtract and multiply decimals.  You know you'd feel a bit empty if you couldn't divide them as well. But something more powerful is going to happen.  If you are like us, you never quite liked those pesky remainders when dividing whole numbers.  Well, those pesky remainders better watch out because they are going to be divided too!!!! Ah ha ha ha ha!!!!!"
